data.description: Nice! Neat! Thrifty! So Much For So Little!!!! Amazing 1,409 square foot home with 4 bedrooms and 2 full baths.  Home also features oversized living room, spacious entry, cute kitchen breakfast nook, indoor laundry, dual pane windows, central heat & air, and 1 year old hot water heater.  Home has been lovingly cared for, for 36 years by the current owner who says the original wood floors are under most of the homes carpet.  The kitchen was remodeled with all the conveniences and modern style. This older home has steel siding and some aluminum for durability and practicality. Both the electrical and plumbing has been updated. The home also features a partial basement providing convenient storage for storing canning and miscellaneous items. The back yard boosts a delicious orange tree, wood deck, 2 storage sheds, and a wood fence with sturdy/tough metal posts meant to last a lifetime.  Must see to appreciate all this timeless beauty has to offer.
